										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">When I dove into the scientific research for my book </span><a href="https://nutritionfacts.org/book/how-not-to-age/"><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">How Not to Age</span></i></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, I uncovered the best ways we can care for our skin as we mature. What are the most important lifestyle factors? The best topical creams? Are there any beneficial procedures? This infographic summarizes the main takeaways.</span></p>
